data.description:
Seller now offering $10,000 concessions to buy down the rate or use towards closing costs with an accepted offer!!
This beautiful mountain retreat sits on a rare 7 acre secluded parcel with stunning rock outcroppings and breathtaking views. Surrounded by a lush woodland of majestic pine and aspen trees, the brand new large Trex deck on the upper level provides panoramic views of Spinney Mountain and down to Buena Vista. Enjoy your morning cup of coffee watching the sunrise and wildlife, and stargazing at night. 
The large kitchen features brand new farmhouse sink, an in-island gas stove, custom cherry cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. The open floor plan connects to a spacious living area with vaulted ceilings and exposed beams, complemented by ample natural light pouring in through the expansive windows, which frame the spectacular view from the deck.The primary bedroom offers a 5-piece ensuite bathroom with an oversized jetted tub and a walk-in closet. Enjoy a picturesque mountain vista through its windows, enhanced by the high vaulted ceilings. The second bedroom features built-in cabinets and desk space, and high-speed internet access is readily available.The walk-out garden level basement can easily be transformed into another bedroom.  
The terraced landscaping invites you to indulge your green thumb. Additional storage is conveniently provided by a shed near the main home. Additionally, there is a 20x20 greenhouse on the property. Stone and Hardie Board siding and the metal roofing helps with fire resistance. 
The house has attached heated two car garage, as well as a detached, oversized two car garage with plenty of room for all your toys and a home gym. Above the attached garage is a large heated room - currently used as the 3rd bedroom and office. Indian Mountain itself provides various amenities, including hiking trails, disc golf, a playground, RV storage, picnic areas, and more.
